summary: Billboards for Tamu75 alternative aspens for use with DynDOLOD or TES5LODGen
descriptionHtml:
[center][/center][size=5][center]Billboards for Tamu75 Alternative Aspens[/center][/size]

[left][/left][center][img]https://68.media.tumblr.com/e376ef28ad6ca2a8cb7bc7c32bef4d0b/tumblr_oqpwctLDQB1s2ptqso2_540.jpg[/img]



[/center][left]Billboards for Tamu75 alternative green aspens allow you to mix in these wonderful trees with other landscape overhauls.


Note: colored versions of Tamu75's trees are featured in Spring Forest Overhaul and were custom made for that mod.  Currently these billboards only come in one color






Install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/62849/?]Tamu75 alternative aspens[/url] after other overhauls (like SFO, Fantasy Forest Overhaul, etc)

Install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/75269/?]vanilla billboards[/url], then billboards for other landscape overhauls, then the Tamu75 billboards

Run [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59721/?]DynDOLOD [/url]or [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/62698/]TES5LODGen  [/url]to generate tree LOD



Check this great tutorial for more info on DynDOLOD

[youtube]1_5MWqeHIzw[/youtube]






CREDITS
Zilav for amazing billboard generator tool
Tamu75 for the wondeful aspens[/left]
